** IMPORTANT ***

	This distribution *MUST* be installed under the /home/mordor 
directory in order to run.  If you want to change this you will have 
to alter src/mtype.h to accomodate the new paths.

--------------- ------ -----

	This distribution can be compiled under Linux, FreeBSD, SunOS and 
requires that you have at least 3M+ RAM (8M+ recommended), networking
capabilities (Ethernet, SLIP, etc), and around 10-15M of HD space. 

